  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game</h2>Eternower is a mazing-focused Tower Defense.<br><br>Minimalistic thematically, opportunistic mechanically.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TD Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Branching - most towers are built through other towers<br></li><li>Pathing focus - always visible and dynamic enemy paths<br></li><li>Viability - supports a range of alternative solutions<br></li><li>Control - game logic is discrete, ensuring reliability</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Message</h2>I hope you have fun.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031790/extras/439a985f1037b001207feff0e76edb35.poster.avif?t=1662018985\" width=464 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031790/extras/439a985f1037b001207feff0e76edb35.webm?t=1662018985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031790/extras/439a985f1037b001207feff0e76edb35.mp4?t=1662018985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
